    "description": "Taiyo Technolex Co.,Ltd. engages in the manufacture and sale of flexible printed circuit in Japan, China, Thailand, rest of Asia, and internationally. It operates through Electronic Board Business, Test System Business, Mirror Polishing Machine Business, and Industrial Machinery Systems Business segments. The company also manufactures and sells electrical inspection machines and visual inspection machines, cylindrical mirror polishing machines, and image processing equipment. It also provides financial appearance inspection system, electrical inspection system, and other products; and electroforming services. In addition, the company engages in Industrial equipment sales business; and provision of manufacturing/system integration. The company was formerly known as Taiyo Industrial Co., LTD. and changed its name to Taiyo Technolex Co.,Ltd. in December 2023. Taiyo Technolex Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1960 and is headquartered in Wakayama, Japan."
